reviewText: If your child is an Olivia and a princess fan, they will love this DVD.  I had fun watching it.  My daughter loved it.

Well, this video has single handedly started a princess obsession in my two year old. She loves this video more than any other Olivia DVD, and she has watched it so much ALREADY that we are back for a second copy due to damage she inflicted on the first copy. This has only been out about 6 weeks.
My Granddaughter loves Olivia.
Bought this for my granddaughter.  She loves it!  Bright and cheery and fun. And since my granddaughters name is Olivia......the opening song is particularly awesome!
Perfect for a 3 year old, who loves Olivia.

My grandkids love this video.  It is the first video they have ever seen, but they really like it.  They ask for it every day- and are allowed to see one episode each day.  They always seem to want to see the one about the princess.  Nice story.

My daughter loves Olivia, and it's hard to find the DVDs in stores. She loves watching this and I was pleased with the price, although the delivery time was longer than expected. I would definitely recommend this for all your little Olivia lovers!
Quick shipping during holiday time, darling product! Granddaughter loved it, took a while though to figure out what she was asking for-I had never heard of Olivia the pig!
My daughters cannot get enough of this DVD! Highly reccomend for anyone who has a daughter(s) that like Olivia and like princesses.
dvd came on time and in excellent shape my granddaughter has enjoyed it over and over again. A good movie
My daughter loves Olivia and this is going to be a great addition to her Easter Basket.  Thanks Easter Bunny!
DVD didn't work.  It was sold as new, but had fingerprints on the bottom.  Because I shipped it as a gift, I couldn't get it back to return it, so I just gave up on it.
My four year old grand daughter watches this movie with her other Olivia movies and is just thrilled that we purchased it for her.

On the cable channel, my grand daughter was transfixed to watch one episode after another. Week days, No Olivia, so that why i decided to buy a couple of DVD's of this character. Once I got the Video's and start playing them, they don't keep her interest. Still trying to figure , why?
She loves the Olivia series and by having the DVD, she can watch it any time from her own room...plus it frees up space on my TiVo.  :)

My daughter owns all of the Olivia dvds and loves them!! This one is no exception!

The stories are cute and entertaining, and the show is not annoying for me, which is a plus. There are too many preschool shows that are hard for me to sit and watch with her, but I enjoy Olivia!

I recommend any of the Olivia dvds or books to parents everywhere! They are always a winner in my household! :)

This DVD of Olivia Princess for a day is well suit for the age groups 1 to 7 years of age.  The animation is done quite well and it displays lessons that children can learn from.  Have purchased other titles for our granddaughter who is also named Olivia
My 3yr granddaughter and 2yr grandson love this movie dvd. Catchy fun easy songs that the kids love to sing along with. stories move along fast enough to keep their attention.

My grandson loves Olivia and so do I!  I wish there were more Olivia DVD's as he now has all of them.  When he comes over for the weekend, we will watch Olivia together and talk about the storyline when each is over.  Olivia, family, and friends are wonderful and provide a very healthy program.  I don't have to worry that my 4 year old grandson will be exposed to something that is not appropriate.  This is a great DVD!

My toddler loves this.  I think she watched the princess episode 100 times in a row before she wanted to watch anything else.  All of the stories are really cute.  Most we had seen on the TV show. The princess episode was a bit different format with lots of singing.
This was a birthday gift for my grand daughter Olivia. She owns all the books and loved this. Bought with one click. It came in plenty of time and was just what she wanted.

My daughter is a huge olivia fan and this is her favorite one by far -the princess for a day one..She watches it over and over. She also liked the tap dance episode on here as well. They others she likes but has seen before on tv. We can't wait for more new episodes!
Appears to be a used DVD, a smudge of dirt on inside cover and minute scratches on DVD surface also did not have that typical annoying seal along edge of case.
Cute book to go along with the Olivia Princess doll.

Got this Olivia DVD super fast & at a great price!
The episodes on here are :
PRINCESS FOR A DAY
OLIVIA'S OLD WEST TREASURE HUNT
OLIVIA PLAYS HOTEL
OLIVIA GOES INTERNATIONAL
OLIVIA TIP TOP TAPPER
OLIVIA BECOMES A CHEF
OLIVIA'S FASHION SHOW
OLIVIA PAINTS A MURAL
great
My daughter loves this movie. It came in brand new condition and has no problems

We love Olivia! Bummed that there were only two seasons made- (right?!) I'm afraid they'll take away the series from Amazon that I have ordered all DVDs. My girls can watch the Princess episode (23 minutes long) a few times a day.
All of these books are tops
Love whole series.
Hard to find! everyone loves Olivia!
My daughter loved it,she watches everyday in the car.
